high_descs: Walk to the counter on the other side of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn left and carry the butter knife to the sink.
Slice a tomato in the sink near the corner.
Move the knife from the tomato to the counter.
Set the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn back to the tomato in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room, turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the tomato slice inside. Open the refrigerator again and take the tomato slice out.
Turn left and walk across the room, turn left again and walk to the sink.
Put the tomato slice on a dish on the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: move forward and turn to the left to face the counter between the sink and the stove
pick up the knife on the edge of the counter that is to the left of the knife with the yellow handle
turn to the left and move to face the sink on the right
slice the tomato that is in the right corner of the sink with the knife
move closer to the counter that is to the right of the sink
put the knife on the counter next to the sink
move to face the sink in front of the sliced tomato
remove a slice of tomato from the sink
turn around, move across the room, turn left moving to face the fridge,
open fridge doors, put the slice of tomato on the right hand side on the left front corner of the top shelf, close the doors, open the doors, remove the tomato slice and close the doors
turn left and move across the room to face the sink
put the tomato slice on the plate that is on the left side of the sink
anns.task_desc: put a cooked slice of tomato on a plate in the sink

high_descs: turn to your left and find a counter top with knives on it
pick up the butter knife next to the yellow knife
take the knife to the sink which is to your left
cut a tomato slice from the tomato in the sink
look at the sink
lay the knife on the counter to the right of the sink
pick up the tomato slice that you cut
turn around and locate the fridge behind you and to the left
carry the tomato slice to the fridge
place the tomato slice in the fridge to chill remove it when chilled
turn around and carry the tomato slice back to the sink
place the sliced tomato in the sink on the left side on top the dish
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of tomato and return it to the sink

high_descs: Turn to the counter on the right
Grab the small knife that is on the counter
Turn left and stop at the sink
Look down at the sink
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the sink
Look down at the sink
Grab one of the tomato slices out of the sink
Turn around and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the tomato in the fridge. Close the door. Open the fridge and take the tomato out
Turn around and head to the sink
Put the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a tomato slice in the sink

high_descs: Go to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the paring knife.
To go the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Stop slicing to tomato.
Place the paring knife on the counter next to the sink.
Look at the sliced tomato.
Take one slice of tomato.
Turn around to go to the refrigerator.
Place the slice of tomato inside the refrigerator to chill and take it out.
Take the chilled slice of tomato back to the sink.
Place the sliced tomato on the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: place a chilled tomato slice on the plate in the sink.
